    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198700/extras/0bddedf12a85f227f17c51f0781088e1.avif?t=1762972802\" width=619 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你肯定玩过贪吃蛇。但你能在黑暗中玩吗？<strong>Snake in the Dark</strong>是对经典街机和解谜游戏（如贪吃蛇和推箱子）的全新演绎。熟悉的有趣玩法，却带来比你预期更多的解谜转折！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>𓆙<u>       吃掉发光！</u>!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198700/extras/6aa873161966876b687ab72ae8265b9a.poster.avif?t=1762972802\" width=618 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198700/extras/6aa873161966876b687ab72ae8265b9a.webm?t=1762972802\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198700/extras/6aa873161966876b687ab72ae8265b9a.mp4?t=1762972802\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>地牢一片漆黑，蛇只能看到前方几步的距离。吃掉魔法光方块可以让你短暂看到整个关卡。墙在哪里？食物在哪里？你的尾巴在哪里？点亮光芒，找出答案！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>𓆙<u>       变大才能赢！</u>!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198700/extras/38258d1cb657700df57461fef03f8f04.poster.avif?t=1762972802\" width=618 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198700/extras/38258d1cb657700df57461fef03f8f04.webm?t=1762972802\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198700/extras/38258d1cb657700df57461fef03f8f04.mp4?t=1762972802\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个关卡的最终目标是同时按下所有压力板开关来打开出口大门，并在门开着时到达出口。蛇太短了？没问题！多吃几个光方块变得更大，就能一次按下所有开关。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>𓆙<u>       推动石头解谜题！</u>!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198700/extras/a35ad9143f0494a86fb9e824e04fa1a0.poster.avif?t=1762972802\" width=618 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198700/extras/a35ad9143f0494a86fb9e824e04fa1a0.webm?t=1762972802\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198700/extras/a35ad9143f0494a86fb9e824e04fa1a0.mp4?t=1762972802\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >看！一个石球！为什么不推动它，用它来压住开关打开门呢？这又是什么？地板上的坑挡住了去路？用另一个石球填满它，制造一座桥让你可以滑过去。用推箱子的方式解决问题！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>𓆙<u>       Snake in the Dark 特色</u>:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >★ 超过100个需要快速思考的街机解谜关卡</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >★ 对贪吃蛇和推箱子等经典游戏机制的全新诠释</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >★ 辉煌的复古图像和音效</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >★ 神秘关卡和隐藏危险</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>𓆙<u>       立即添加愿望单并关注！</u></strong></h2>",
